title: Tinsect
desc:
- Can be played on <:wild:1106237191388143838>/Wild-Adjacent cards, <:gray:1107516393450127411> and <:yellow:1106234135384699023>.
- <:tinsect:1172249217272643604>s will not have their effect on play
- After every turn, a <:tinsect:1172249217272643604> on the play pile will discard the card played before it.
- When a <:tinsect:1172249217272643604> is on a card that it could have been played on again, it will do its effect on the card.
